Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但后来有想了想  算了吧  不值得
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Didn't do it.
