Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- What car? - My car, of course. Where is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-什么车？-当然是我的车  在哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A tow truck removed it. They gave us an address.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拖车把它拖走了  他们给了一个地址
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The police gave mom a piece of paper with the address.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}警察给了妈妈一张纸  上面写着地址
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Pick up that paper. We'll get the car.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去拿到那张纸  我们去取车
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Now? - Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-现在吗？-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But you just left intensive care.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是你刚从重症监护室出来
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They took you to a room, and you almost regained your consciousness.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们带你去了一个房间  差不多已经恢复意识了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- So? - You mumbled something but we didn't hear.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-然后呢？-你喃喃自语但我们没听清
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How? What did I say?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么说？我怎么说？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A cat named Munir or something. You asked about him.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一只叫尼穆尔的猫还是什么的  你问到过它
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You asked if we fed him. - Huh.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你问我们有没有给它喂食 -嗯……
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Grandpa. Don't you remember anything?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爷爷  你什么都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How you came to the hospital?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你怎么到医院来的？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You had an angiogram.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你做了血管造影
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I remember. I remember everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我记得  我都记得
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.32,0:07:06.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Come, let's get the car. - What will you do with it?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.32,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-来吧  让我们去取车 -你取车做什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't leave the car there. It's a memento from Mebrure.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不能把车停在那里  那是梅布鲁雷留给我的纪念品
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's your grandma's car. Come on.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是你奶奶的车  来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly. This way.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这边走
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- There goes my head again. - Evening, sir.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我的头疼又来了-先生  晚上好
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good evening, son. Take me slowly.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}晚上好  小伙子  慢点走
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Okay. What's wrong? - My head's spinning.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-怎么了？-我的头好晕
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The doctor says walk, but what good is walking?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}医生说要多走路  走路有什么好处？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Your slippers... Where are we going?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你没穿拖鞋……我们去哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- We'll get the keys. - Grandpa...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我们去拿钥匙 -爷爷
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Dad.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Dad, are you awake? I'll alert the nurses.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸  你醒了  我去叫护士
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- No, mom. The nurses know. - They do?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-不用  妈妈  护士已经知道了 -他们知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They told him to rest. The doctor will see him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们叫他先休息  医生明天再来看他
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm all right, sweetie.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我很好  亲爱的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You gave us such a scare.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你吓到我们了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What were you doing there at that time of night?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}晚上的时候你在那儿干什么?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On the other side of the city.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在城市的另一边
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You left the house, and didn't tell us anything.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你离开家  什么都没告诉我们
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where were you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你去哪里了？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I don't know how to tell you this.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不知道该怎么开口
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.36,0:10:03.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I could have said before... Somehow.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.36,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我应该早点告诉你们的……
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You have the right to know.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你们应该知道
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}People sometimes
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}人啊  有时候
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}go into a wholly different mood.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会陷入完全不同的状态
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.68,0:10:22.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They do things they wouldn't dream of.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.68,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}做他们梦寐以求的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even I can't recognize myself sometimes.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有时候甚至我都不认识自己
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering how I'd done something.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想着自己为什么会做这些事
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But I did.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是我还是做了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They happened. All of it.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}都做了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'd hear about it one day, anyway.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你们总有一天会听说的
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd rather you hear it from me than anybody else.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我宁愿你们听我说  而不是听别人说
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And then...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}然后……
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's your decision, my child.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}决定权在你们  孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm your father. And I'm your grandfather.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是你的父亲  我是你的祖父
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't you forget that, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘记这点  好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm in love, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我恋爱了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You're in love? - I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你恋爱了吗 -我交了一个女朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was at her place that night.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那天晚上我在她家
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was on my way back.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在回去的路上
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You were on your way...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你在路上
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What are you saying, dad?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸  你在说什么
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- We made love until morning. - Ew! What?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我们做爱直到天明 -呕！什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Key's still in the ignition, mate!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}钥匙还插着呢！
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You know how to drive? - We won't be driving it.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你会开车吗？-我们不开它
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- What will we do? - We'll wreck it to shit.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-那我们干嘛？-我们要搞坏它
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sit down. You're making me dizzy.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}坐下  你把我晃晕了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And? What happened to the courthouse?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么？法院发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Who burned it down? - It looks like the mob, for now.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-谁把它烧了？-目前看来是黑帮做的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看我说什么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We had a bet.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们打赌
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't celebrate yet. It's not certain.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}别高兴的太早  还没确定呢
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I think that man, Tufan, did it.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我认为是那个叫图凡的男人做的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But that man, I don't know...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是那个男人  我不清楚……
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Clean since he got out of jail.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他出狱之后做事一直很干净
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What did he has to do with that judge?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他和那个法官有什么关系？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If only I knew.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要是知道就好了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我告诉你
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.48,0:13:57.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If there's no ties between the victim and the killer,
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.48,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果受害者和杀手之间没有联系  
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}then it's a hired gun, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那很可能是借刀杀人  亲爱的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's conducting somebody else's business.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他在给做别人的事
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.76,0:14:08.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.76,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喂？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.76,0:14:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.76,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在哪？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On my way.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我这就过去
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Another body, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又一具尸体  对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}See you later.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我走了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Who's heard of a letter with one sentence?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁写信只写一句话？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That son of a bitch will keep writing. Nevra!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那个凶手会继续写的  内芙拉!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.84,0:14:33.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What is it, dad?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.84,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸爸  怎么了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The man's writing for you to read it.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这个男人在写给你看
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Yeah, so? - So you write him back.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-是  然后呢？ -你给他回信
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The doctor will be here to see you in half an hour.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}医生会在半小时之内过来给你检查
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I hope he comes soon and lets me go. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望他快点来  让我回家  我很累
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In bed all day, with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}整天躺在床上  无所事事
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.88,0:14:55.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You didn't bring anything to read, either.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.88,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你也没带任何书可以读
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where's your mom?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你妈妈呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Out. Eating something.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在外面吃饭
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You have money? - I do.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你有钱吗？-我有
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Get me something to read.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去买本书来给我看
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Okay, but... - There has to be a bookstore.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-可以  但是 -这附近肯定有书店
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll wait for the doctor.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要等医生过来
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No, no. You go now. Now.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  不  你现在去
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Let me take you to your room. - I can go myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我带你回房间-我可以自己走
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You go, son.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你去吧  孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- But what do you want me to buy? - Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你要我买什么书？-嗯……
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The book is called Life Is Traffic. Buy me that.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}书名叫做《人生就是交通》
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Okay. - Go ahead.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-好的 -去吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Get better soon. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-祝你早日康复 -谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.32,0:16:29.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Terrible thing, being ill.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.32,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生病太可怕了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I hope you get well soon.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望你早日康复
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm also...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也……
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He won't wake up.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他听不见的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Huh.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哦
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Okay then.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Have a good day.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你有美好的一天
Dialogue: 2,0:17:05.52,0:17:09.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I'm here to visit him. - You don't say?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:05.52,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我是来拜访他的 -真的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How do you know him?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你怎么认识他的？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I ONLY TRUST HER. BECAUSE NEVRA UNDERSTANDS ME.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只相信她  因为内芙拉了解我
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Are those your brothers? - Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-那是你的兄弟们吗？-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And what do they do?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- They get high. - That much is clear.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-他们长得很高 -是的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.96,0:18:14.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- And they make kites. - Was the car right there?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.96,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-他们会做风筝 -汽车在那儿吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No. It was over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  在那边
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All right, kid. Take the boy.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好吧  孩子 把他带走吧
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Must've been followed. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-一定是被人跟踪了 -是的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Another casing, sir.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又找到一个  先生
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.12,0:18:37.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Did his job with one bullet in his first. Now fired six times.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.12,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}第一次只用了一颗子弹  这次用了六颗
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then again, he also shot an aquarium in the first one.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并且他还在第一次射中了鱼缸
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The victim has two entry wounds.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}受害人有两处伤口
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Did his eyesight go bad all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他的视力突然下降了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Victim's ID info.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}受害者的身份证信息
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Answer, damn it.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}接电话 该死
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.08,0:19:38.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good, very good. You found some tire tracks, great.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.08,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}非常好  发现了一些轮胎痕迹  太好了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Finger prints, too. Well done.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还有指纹  干的漂亮
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Footprints for the next murder, you say?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}下次谋杀时再找个脚印  你说怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's already an ongoing country-wide search for him.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}已经在全国范围内搜寻他了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And what good is the search?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有什么用处吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He kills right under our noses.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他在我们眼皮底下杀人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If he was afraid of getting caught,
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果他害怕被抓住
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}he wouldn't lay his cards on the table.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}绝对不会摊牌
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He knows he won't be caught.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他知道他不会被抓到
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So there's only one way to catch him: 
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因此  只有一种方法可以抓住他：
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Find out why he's committing the murders.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找出他为什么要杀人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Otherwise you'll go door to door, asking to yourselves where he is.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不然你就挨家挨户自己去找他
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Here.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给你
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You, my office.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你来我办公室
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I spoke with the prosecutor today.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我今天和检察官谈过了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.23,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He doesn't want you involved in this whatsoever.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他不想让你卷入这件事
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He told me to take you out of this case.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我把你调走
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.35,0:20:41.47,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I said "Okay, but maybe the Nevra on the labels is a different person."
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.35,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我说：“好吧  但也许标签上写的内芙拉是另外一个人”
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We must take precautions, he says. 
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他说们必须采取预防措施
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.27,0:20:49.15,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He asks if there's a difference between Nevra and anybody else.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.27,0:20:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他问内芙拉跟其他人是否有区别  
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told him how much difference it made for me.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我告诉他你对我有多重要
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told him what a great police officer you can be.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我告诉他你可以成为一名伟大的警察
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In conclusion, he told me to do what I must.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最后  他让我放手去做
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you know what this means? 
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道这是意味着什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If the Nevra this killer is talking about...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果凶手说的内芙拉……
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}is the same Nevra sitting across the table right now,
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和现在坐在我对面的内芙拉是同一个人
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}and you learn about this, and don't tell me,
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道  并且不告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}you can't be a police anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你就不能再做警察了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Understood, Chief.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明白  长官
Dialogue: 2,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Out.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}出去吧
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.60,0:21:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.60,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have an idea.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我有个主意
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.96,0:22:02.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm going mad. I'm about to lose my mind.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.96,0:22:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要疯了……
Dialogue: 2,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where is this man?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他去哪了？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:04.48,0:22:06.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He left his phone, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:04.48,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还把手机留下了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He doesn't use it, anyway.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他不用手机
Dialogue: 2,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What's this book he asked you to buy so urgently?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他叫你这么急着买的那本书是什么书?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No idea.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不知道……
Dialogue: 2,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Life Is Traffic, by Nukhet Coban.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生活就是交通  作者：努赫特·科班
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.72,0:22:30.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hi. This is Agah's room, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.72,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嗨  这是阿加的病房 对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Agah, my boy. 
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}老弟
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What are you up to now?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你在干嘛呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.48,0:22:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Our department had this guy, Zekai.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.48,0:22:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们部门有个叫泽凯的人
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Such a sweet man.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真是个好人
Dialogue: 2,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He had a son who caught pneumonia.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他儿子得了肺炎
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Very severe.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}非常严重
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Doctors said he wouldn't live. What could Zekai do?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}医生说他儿子快不行了  但泽凯又能做什么呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He lost all hope on doctors.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他对医生失去希望了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.36,0:22:55.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He visited holy sepulchers, made offerings.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.36,0:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他拜访圣墓教堂  供奉祭品。
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.56,0:23:02.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The boy they said would die, miraculously recovered.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.56,0:23:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那个医生说快死掉的孩子  竟然奇迹般恢复过来
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zekai, of course, went to make his offering.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然了  泽凯又去供奉
Dialogue: 2,0:23:07.04,0:23:12.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's made a vow to make nine paupers happy.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:07.04,0:23:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他发誓要让九个穷人幸福
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.84,0:23:16.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because his son was nine. Whatever...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.84,0:23:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为他儿子才九岁  不管怎样……
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He goes to a poor neighborhood.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他去了贫民窟
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.68,0:23:21.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}His money's ready.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.68,0:23:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}带足了钱
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He gives the money away.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他把钱送了出去
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Makes nine paupers happy.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让九个穷人幸福起来
Dialogue: 2,0:23:29.08,0:23:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A tenth pauper appears. "I'm poor, too." he says.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:29.08,0:23:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是第十个穷人出现了  说：“我也很穷！”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zekai says he's out of money, but the guy won't believe him.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}泽凯说他已经没有钱了  但是那人不相信他
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.92,0:23:42.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"You gave a fortune away, where's mine?" he asks.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.92,0:23:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“你给出去了一大笔钱  我的呢？”他问
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.16,0:23:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- And stabs Zekai. - Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.16,0:23:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-然后刺杀了泽凯 -哦  天啊
Dialogue: 2,0:23:46.64,0:23:48.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Such a pity.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:46.64,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真的很遗憾
Dialogue: 2,0:23:48.16,0:23:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:48.16,0:23:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}确实
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.88,0:23:54.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But then, you understand the tenth pauper.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.88,0:23:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是  第十个穷人可以理解
Dialogue: 2,0:23:54.36,0:23:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:54.36,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:23:56.72,0:23:59.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You give money to everybody, and when it's his turn...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:56.72,0:23:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你给所有人发钱  但轮到他时……
Dialogue: 2,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This happens sometimes. I mean...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这种情况时有发生  我是说……
Dialogue: 2,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a crime, but not a criminal.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是犯罪  但他却不是罪犯
Dialogue: 2,0:24:06.04,0:24:07.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hello there.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:06.04,0:24:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你好
Dialogue: 2,0:24:08.48,0:24:11.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Agah, sir? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:08.48,0:24:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}阿加  先生  您在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:11.80,0:24:14.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Why? - Everyone's looking for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:11.80,0:24:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-怎么了？-每个人都在找你
Dialogue: 2,0:24:23.40,0:24:25.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Has Zuhal left? - Who?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:23.40,0:24:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-祖哈尔离开了吗？-谁？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.76,0:24:30.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I'll go. - Were you staying here?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.76,0:24:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我这就去 -你也住在这里吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.76,0:24:34.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Agah, visit me some time! - Like hell I will. It's your fault.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.76,0:24:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-阿加  有空过来玩！-来个屁  都怪你！
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.72,0:24:45.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hello, Ates? Can you talk?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.72,0:24:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喂  阿提斯  你方便说话吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:47.48,0:24:50.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yeah, I'm at work. At the department.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:47.48,0:24:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是的  我局里上班
Dialogue: 2,0:24:50.92,0:24:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's this thing. Urgent. Could you come here?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:50.92,0:24:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有个急事  你能来一趟吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:58.48,0:25:01.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nothing to worry about. Come. I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:58.48,0:25:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不用担心  来吧  我等你
Dialogue: 2,0:25:45.96,0:25:50.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Sorry. I had a thing. - I'm sorry I couldn't come.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:45.96,0:25:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-对不起  我来晚了-对不起  我不能过去
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.44,0:25:52.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}To your department, I mean.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.44,0:25:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的部门  我是说……
Dialogue: 2,0:25:53.24,0:25:55.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They don't like me over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:53.24,0:25:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的同事不太喜欢我
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.04,0:25:58.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's as close as I can get.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.04,0:25:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我尽量帮你
Dialogue: 2,0:26:01.08,0:26:02.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:01.08,0:26:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这个给你
Dialogue: 2,0:26:03.48,0:26:04.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:03.48,0:26:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:26:05.88,0:26:07.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's cold, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:05.88,0:26:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有点凉了
Dialogue: 2,0:26:09.12,0:26:10.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:09.12,0:26:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我就是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:26:11.00,0:26:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Workaholic. Coffees went cold all the time.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:11.00,0:26:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}工作狂  咖啡经常放凉
Dialogue: 2,0:26:15.08,0:26:17.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I may not look like it but I used to be
Dialogue: 2,0:26:15.08,0:26:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可能看起来不像  但我曾经是
Dialogue: 2,0:26:18.24,0:26:21.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}a fiery and an idealist reporter.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:18.24,0:26:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一位热情的理想主义者记者
Dialogue: 2,0:26:21.72,0:26:23.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was a police reporter, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:21.72,0:26:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也是一名警察记者
Dialogue: 2,0:26:24.04,0:26:25.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I don't about the fire,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:24.04,0:26:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不热情
Dialogue: 2,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but there's still some idealism left.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是还有一些理想主义
Dialogue: 2,0:26:28.36,0:26:30.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Otherwise why would you come all this way, no?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:28.36,0:26:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不然你为什么要大老远来  不是吗?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:32.00,0:26:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Maybe I just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:32.00,0:26:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也许我只是想见你
Dialogue: 2,0:26:34.16,0:26:35.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Why not?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:34.16,0:26:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么不？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:36.56,0:26:40.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Maybe it's two birds with one stone. Why not?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:36.56,0:26:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也许是一石二鸟吧  为什么不呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.64,0:26:42.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Never.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.64,0:26:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是的
Dialogue: 2,0:26:45.04,0:26:47.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As I am still carrying that idealism,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:45.04,0:26:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我仍然怀着理想主义  
Dialogue: 2,0:26:49.56,0:26:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I am also carrying a stone for each bird.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:49.56,0:26:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我还为每只鸟背着一块石头
Dialogue: 2,0:26:59.08,0:27:01.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- What's this? - It's a story.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:59.08,0:27:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-这是什么？-是一篇文章
Dialogue: 2,0:27:02.16,0:27:03.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Can you publish it?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:02.16,0:27:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可以出版吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.48,0:27:08.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"An anonymous law enforcement source."
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.48,0:27:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“匿名执法来源”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:09.56,0:27:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Exactly that. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:09.56,0:27:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-正是 -嗯
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.36,0:27:15.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I gave you this. You're giving it back.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.36,0:27:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我给了你  你又还给了我
Dialogue: 2,0:27:17.60,0:27:19.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}To me, that's romantic.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:17.60,0:27:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对我来说很浪漫
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.32,0:27:24.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- The sooner the better. - All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.32,0:27:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-越快越好 -好的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:25.80,0:27:27.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll post it online.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:25.80,0:27:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会在网上发布
Dialogue: 2,0:27:29.24,0:27:30.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Had a look at the courthouse yet?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:29.24,0:27:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你调查法院了吗
Dialogue: 2,0:27:31.00,0:27:32.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I did, but it's a dead end.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:31.00,0:27:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}查了  但那是死胡同
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.80,0:27:42.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I could send you to an entirely different street.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.80,0:27:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以送你去一条完全不同的街道
Dialogue: 2,0:27:43.28,0:27:45.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Your dead judge...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:43.28,0:27:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那个死掉的法官
Dialogue: 2,0:27:45.84,0:27:48.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All his cases involved some sort of bribery.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:45.84,0:27:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他经手的所有案件都涉及某种贿赂
Dialogue: 2,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Public knowledge, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}众所周知
Dialogue: 2,0:27:50.36,0:27:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Might as well have invoiced them.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:50.36,0:27:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很可能都有发票
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.12,0:27:54.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you were to look at...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.12,0:27:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你想知道……
Dialogue: 2,0:27:55.56,0:27:58.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}whose lives he'd ruined in those cases,
Dialogue: 2,0:27:55.56,0:27:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他在这些案件中毁掉了谁的生活
Dialogue: 2,0:27:58.68,0:28:00.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}maybe you'll find something.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:58.68,0:28:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也许你会发现一些东西
Dialogue: 2,0:28:02.92,0:28:04.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But his record is spotless.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:02.92,0:28:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是他的记录一尘不染
Dialogue: 2,0:28:08.04,0:28:12.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then for one time only,
Dialogue: 2,0:28:08.04,0:28:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只有一次
Dialogue: 2,0:28:12.80,0:28:14.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}he didn't take a bribe...
Dialogue: 2,0:28:12.80,0:28:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他没有受贿
Dialogue: 2,0:28:15.48,0:28:17.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But gave a bribe.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:15.48,0:28:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而是行贿
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.24,0:28:25.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Use your other medicine. They won't cause a problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.24,0:28:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}服用另外一种药  那样不会造成任何问题
Dialogue: 2,0:28:26.08,0:28:29.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But sir, you have to let your daughter know.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:26.08,0:28:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是先生  你得让你的女儿知道
Dialogue: 2,0:28:29.60,0:28:31.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:29.60,0:28:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然
Dialogue: 2,0:28:32.28,0:28:34.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I must accept it first.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:32.28,0:28:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我必须先接受
Dialogue: 2,0:28:34.28,0:28:36.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I'll tell them both.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:34.28,0:28:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}然后再告诉他们两个
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.64,0:28:38.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Alzheimer's is a serious condition.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.64,0:28:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}老年痴呆症是很严重的病
Dialogue: 2,0:28:40.72,0:28:43.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Tailor-made for a serious man like myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:40.72,0:28:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为像我这样严肃的人量身定做的
Dialogue: 2,0:28:44.84,0:28:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where were you this morning?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:44.84,0:28:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天早上你在哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:46.32,0:28:47.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Your daughter worried about you.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:46.32,0:28:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的女儿很担心你
Dialogue: 2,0:28:49.40,0:28:51.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The night I had a heart attack,
Dialogue: 2,0:28:49.40,0:28:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我心脏病发作的那天晚上
Dialogue: 2,0:28:52.60,0:28:54.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I had a sharp pain right here.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:52.60,0:28:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在这里剧烈疼痛
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.72,0:28:58.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I said, "Agah, this is it. You're leaving this life."
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.72,0:28:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我说：“阿加  就是这样  你将要走完这一生”
Dialogue: 2,0:29:00.36,0:29:02.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}First thing I thought about
Dialogue: 2,0:29:00.36,0:29:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我首先想到的是
Dialogue: 2,0:29:02.80,0:29:05.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}was what my daughter and grandson was going to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:02.80,0:29:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我女儿和孙子要怎么办
Dialogue: 2,0:29:06.44,0:29:07.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What would become of them?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:06.44,0:29:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们会怎样？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.04,0:29:11.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So interesting.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.04,0:29:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很有趣
Dialogue: 2,0:29:12.12,0:29:15.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So long as man doesn't understand that he's dying,
Dialogue: 2,0:29:12.12,0:29:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果人不知道自己快死了
Dialogue: 2,0:29:15.76,0:29:19.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}he doesn't think about those he's leaving behind.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:15.76,0:29:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就不会去想他的后人
Dialogue: 2,0:29:19.12,0:29:20.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I called my lawyer.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:19.12,0:29:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我打电话给我的律师
Dialogue: 2,0:29:21.28,0:29:23.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Told him to leave them everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:21.28,0:29:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}告诉他把一切都留给家人
Dialogue: 2,0:29:23.40,0:29:25.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They shouldn't have to deal with the inheritance stuff.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:23.40,0:29:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们不必处理继承的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:29:25.76,0:29:28.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was busy with those things.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:25.76,0:29:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}早上我在忙那些事情
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.16,0:29:30.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't want to make them sad, and didn't tell them.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.16,0:29:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想让他们难过  所以并没有告诉他们
Dialogue: 2,0:29:33.48,0:29:34.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Come in, please.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:33.48,0:29:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请进来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.12,0:29:40.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's get to the point.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.12,0:29:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们言归正传
Dialogue: 2,0:29:40.60,0:29:43.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'll be our guest for another day.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:40.60,0:29:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你要在我们这里多住一天
Dialogue: 2,0:29:43.08,0:29:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:43.08,0:29:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- 好吗？好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.00,0:29:48.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- All right. Get well soon. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.00,0:29:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-好的  祝早日康复 -谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:29:54.12,0:29:55.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You made us leave.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:54.12,0:29:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你让我们离开
Dialogue: 2,0:29:55.76,0:29:57.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I couldn't ask while he's here.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:55.76,0:29:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他在这里的时候我不能问
Dialogue: 2,0:29:57.84,0:30:00.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What's this thing you can't share with us?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:57.84,0:30:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么事不能让我们听到？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:02.64,0:30:05.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know about the heart attack I had, sweetie?
Dialogue: 2,0:30:02.64,0:30:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道我得了心脏病吧  亲爱的？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:07.20,0:30:11.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I asked the doctor about my sexual life this point on.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:07.20,0:30:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我刚才咨询医生一些关于性生活的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:30:12.44,0:30:13.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Now you know.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:12.44,0:30:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在你知道了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:14.48,0:30:16.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Would you have liked to listen?
Dialogue: 2,0:30:14.48,0:30:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你想听吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:22.68,0:30:24.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I could stay.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:22.68,0:30:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想留下来
Dialogue: 2,0:30:25.00,0:30:27.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No, you go home and rest.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:25.00,0:30:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  你回家休息
Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.68,0:30:29.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We'll be back tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.68,0:30:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们明天还会回来
Dialogue: 2,0:30:29.68,0:30:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Dad called today.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:29.68,0:30:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸爸今天打电话了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:32.60,0:30:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Finally, huh.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:32.60,0:30:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}终于……
Dialogue: 2,0:30:34.80,0:30:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Finally he must've understand what he's done.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:34.80,0:30:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他总算想清楚他做了什么
Dialogue: 2,0:30:38.32,0:30:40.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Doesn't have the face to call me, either.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:38.32,0:30:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没脸给我打电话了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:40.48,0:30:42.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So he called you. What is he saying?
Dialogue: 2,0:30:40.48,0:30:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以他打给你  他在说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:43.52,0:30:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He filed for divorce.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:43.52,0:30:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他提出要离婚
Dialogue: 2,0:30:48.08,0:30:49.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:48.08,0:30:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊
Dialogue: 2,0:30:49.84,0:30:51.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's a relief.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:49.84,0:30:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}解脱了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:51.68,0:30:52.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Really. I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:51.68,0:30:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真的  我解脱了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:53.60,0:30:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I mean...
Dialogue: 2,0:30:53.60,0:30:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是说……
Dialogue: 2,0:30:55.84,0:30:57.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's a load off my shoulder.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:55.84,0:30:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我肩上的重担终于能放下了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:57.56,0:30:58.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm happy.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:57.56,0:30:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我很高兴
Dialogue: 2,0:30:59.24,0:31:00.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So happy.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:59.24,0:31:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很高兴
Dialogue: 2,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Finally, that's done.
Dialogue: 2,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}终于结束了
Dialogue: 2,0:31:04.40,0:31:07.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Mom, you're fine, right? - Why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 2,0:31:04.40,0:31:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-妈妈  你还好吧？-我为什么不好呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:52.76,0:32:54.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good night.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:52.76,0:32:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}晚安
Dialogue: 2,0:33:09.00,0:33:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}That's not me.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:09.00,0:33:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是我
Dialogue: 2,0:33:11.20,0:33:12.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}It's some other Nevra Elmas.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:11.20,0:33:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是其他的内芙拉 ·埃尔马斯
Dialogue: 2,0:33:14.48,0:33:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Or like Firuz had said,{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:14.48,0:33:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}或像菲鲁兹所说的那样  
Dialogue: 2,0:33:16.16,0:33:19.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}he must have seen me on TV or the newspaper, and is addressing me.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:16.16,0:33:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他一定在电视或报纸上见过我  并且在跟我沟通
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.04,0:33:25.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That may be. But the real question is
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.04,0:33:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也许是这样  但真正的问题是
Dialogue: 2,0:33:25.76,0:33:28.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}not whom he's writing, but why he's writing.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:25.76,0:33:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是他在给谁写  而是他为什么在写
Dialogue: 2,0:33:28.80,0:33:30.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I think he's alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:28.80,0:33:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我觉得他很孤独
Dialogue: 2,0:33:30.32,0:33:33.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Crippling from it, in fact.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:30.32,0:33:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}实际上是很严重的孤独
Dialogue: 2,0:33:33.44,0:33:34.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}No one to speak with.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:33.44,0:33:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没人跟他说话
