Dialogue: 2,0:33:35.88,0:33:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使他说了  也没人听
Dialogue: 2,0:33:39.28,0:33:41.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He wants to be listened to so badly,
Dialogue: 2,0:33:39.28,0:33:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他非常渴望被倾听
Dialogue: 2,0:33:42.32,0:33:44.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}he's willing to kill for it.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:42.32,0:33:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他愿意为此而杀人
Dialogue: 2,0:33:50.52,0:33:53.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}MISSING SUSPECT
Dialogue: 2,0:33:50.52,0:33:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}寻找嫌犯
Dialogue: 2,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Who could be that lonely?{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁会那么孤独？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:25.16,0:34:27.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zuhal? Darling?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:25.16,0:34:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祖哈尔？亲爱的？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:04.24,0:37:06.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mister? Mister?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:04.24,0:37:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}先生？先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:08.84,0:37:10.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you okay, mister?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:08.84,0:37:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}先生  你还好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:16.04,0:37:18.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Peace be with you. - And also with you.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:16.04,0:37:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-和平与你同在 -也与你同在
Dialogue: 2,0:37:18.96,0:37:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What brought you here, at this hour?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:18.96,0:37:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这个时候来这里有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:20.92,0:37:23.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've come to take my car. They towed it here.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:20.92,0:37:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我来取我的车  他们把车拖到这里了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:23.40,0:37:24.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:23.40,0:37:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天来
Dialogue: 2,0:37:25.00,0:37:27.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No. Tomorrow won't do.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:25.00,0:37:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天不行的
Dialogue: 2,0:37:27.12,0:37:29.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm coming from the hospital. I have somebody sick.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:27.12,0:37:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我从医院过来的  我有个朋友生病了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:29.48,0:37:32.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have to take the car there, and go to their hometown.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:29.48,0:37:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我必须要取车  然后开车去他家
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.60,0:37:35.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish them well. Where are you from?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.60,0:37:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望他没事  你来自哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:40.84,0:37:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Mister. Are you feeling better? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:40.84,0:37:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-先生  您感觉好些吗？-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:37:45.00,0:37:47.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We've called an ambulance. They'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:45.00,0:37:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们叫了一辆救护车他们很快到这里
Dialogue: 2,0:37:48.76,0:37:49.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:48.76,0:37:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:50.80,0:37:51.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:50.80,0:37:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你在说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:51.88,0:37:53.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- In the car. - What's there?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:51.88,0:37:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-车里……-有什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:57.00,0:37:58.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In the bag...
Dialogue: 2,0:37:57.00,0:37:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在包里……
Dialogue: 2,0:37:58.20,0:37:59.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- What's there? - In the bag...
Dialogue: 2,0:37:58.20,0:37:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-里面有什么？-包里……
Dialogue: 2,0:38:05.84,0:38:07.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mister...
Dialogue: 2,0:38:05.84,0:38:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}先生……
Dialogue: 2,0:38:08.44,0:38:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Mister. - In the car...
Dialogue: 2,0:38:08.44,0:38:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-先生 -在车上
Dialogue: 2,0:38:10.20,0:38:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- What? - My car.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:10.20,0:38:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-什么？-我的车
Dialogue: 2,0:39:44.52,0:39:47.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This second murder is really making national headlines.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:44.52,0:39:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}第二起谋杀案已经成为全国头条新闻
Dialogue: 2,0:39:49.52,0:39:53.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}While the nationwide search for the killer, Tufan Elibol, is still ongoing,
Dialogue: 2,0:39:49.52,0:39:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管在全国范围内搜寻杀手图凡 埃利博尔仍在进行中  
Dialogue: 2,0:39:53.24,0:39:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}it is believed that he may not be acting alone,
Dialogue: 2,0:39:53.24,0:39:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但人们相信他可能不是独自作案
Dialogue: 2,0:39:56.08,0:39:59.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}and that he may have two or three accomplices.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:56.08,0:39:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可能有两个或三个同伙
