Dialogue: 2,0:40:05.76,0:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这些谋杀可能与图凡 埃利博尔无关
Dialogue: 2,0:40:09.80,0:40:13.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Indeed, dear viewers, he may be a victim of them.
