Dialogue: 2,0:41:01.76,0:41:02.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:41:01.76,0:41:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嘿!
