Dialogue: 2,0:44:51.60,0:44:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当电梯卡在两层楼之间时  
Dialogue: 2,0:44:54.64,0:44:56.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}press on the call button once.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:54.64,0:44:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}按下通话按钮一次
