Dialogue: 2,0:44:57.32,0:44:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果它不动
Dialogue: 2,0:44:59.36,0:45:02.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}it's something only the mechanic could fix.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:59.36,0:45:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就是只有修理工能解决的问题  
Dialogue: 2,0:45:04.84,0:45:06.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't kill you here.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:04.84,0:45:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不能在这里杀了你
