Dialogue: 2,0:45:20.04,0:45:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好了  让我来说下怎么办
Dialogue: 2,0:45:24.40,0:45:25.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll press this button once.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:24.40,0:45:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会按一次这个按钮
